subtitleNullable: Popularity of Cocktails through the years 2001 to 2021
descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains information about the number of website visits for cocktails throughout the years 2001 to 2021 on the site "http://bar.leo.org/bar_de.html". It is in a long format. The top 10 cocktails with the most visitors are listed for each year and for each month.

In many cases, there was no data for the month in which case it was omitted.
